      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户旅程图，场景是用户发现感兴趣的课程session然后把它克隆到自己的日程里。整体分成Dashboard、Feed和Planner三个主要阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dashboard",
        "Feed",
        "Planner",
        "section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个阶段。那Dashboard阶段用户具体做什么？是直接进入Feed浏览吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dashboard",
        "section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Dashboard阶段其实比较简单，用户只是打开一个feed preview，满意度大概5分吧，算是浅层接触。真正的discover动作是在Feed阶段完成的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dashboard",
        "Open feed preview",
        "Feed",
        "discover"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Dashboard和Feed两个section搭好，Feed下面放browse public sessions和select a session这两个步骤，满意度都标7分，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Feed",
        "Browse public sessions",
        "Select a session"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。然后最关键的一步是clone into planner，这个满意度要高一些，9分，因为用户找到了想要的内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Clone into planner",
        "Planner"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加clone into planner。那Planner阶段还有什么？用户调整完细节保存之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Planner",
        "Adjust details & save"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后一步是系统反馈：session被添加到personal schedule，这个也是9分，让用户有明确的完成感。整个journey的title就叫\"Discover & Clone a Session\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Session added to personal schedule",
